SUMMARY:Neon Null (PC (Microsoft Windows))
DESCRIPTION:Reality is collapsing into the Null\, a digital void that consu
 mes entire sectors of existence. As the last surviving pilot\, you dive in
 to corrupted space to fight through hostile anomalies\, recover lost data\
 , and uncover the force behind the collapse before everything is erased.\n
 \nEvery run presents a new challenge. Enemy formations\, hazards\, and upg
 rade opportunities shift from one attempt to the next\, forcing you to adj
 ust your strategy on the fly. Powerful builds can emerge quickly\, but a s
 ingle mistake can end a run just as fast.\n\nProgress doesn't stop when yo
 u fail. Unlock new upgrades\, expand your arsenal\, and discover abilities
  that open new ways to approach future runs. Each attempt helps you push f
 arther\, survive longer\, and tackle increasingly difficult encounters.\n\
 nBuilt around responsive controls and rapid-fire action\, Neon Null reward
 s skill\, experimentation\, and persistence. The farther you travel into t
 he fractured cosmos\, the more dangerous and unpredictable it becomes.\n\n
 https://www.igdb.com/games/neon-null
END:VEVENT
