 al of wacky weapons and gadgets. Throw TNT across the map\, blast firework
 s and rockets into your rivals\, or smash them with Thor’s hammer. Pull ou
 t blasters\, revolvers\, and all sorts of outrageous guns\, or go full sci
 -fi and deflect attacks with a lightsaber.\n\nPotions add another layer of
  madness\, letting you grow huge\, shrink tiny\, run faster\, or hit harde
 r — flipping the fight in unexpected ways.\n\nEvery map is a sandbox of de
 struction\, packed with hazards\, traps\, and interactive elements you can
  turn against your opponents. From launching rivals sky-high to chaining e
 xplosions together\, no two matches ever play the same.\n\nWhether you’re 
 dodging rockets\, spamming explosives\, or laughing as your friends fall i
 nto the void\, Knockout Battle guarantees non-stop action\, hilarious mome
 nts\, and pure chaos. And of course… expect a ridiculous amount of explosi
 ons and rockets.\n\nhttps://www.igdb.com/games/knockout-battle
