DTSTAMP:20260706T210613Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260901
SUMMARY:Aion 2 (PC (Microsoft Windows))
DESCRIPTION:Aion 2 takes place 200 years after the PC game\, Aion: The Towe
 r of Eternity.\n\nOne main feature is the appearance of dimensional cracks
 \, allowing players from different servers to engage in large-scale PVP. G
 liding and wings will no doubt be there as the IP’s signature element. NCs
 oft even claimed Aion 2 will have features which could not be realized in 
 the PC game\, and that its vision for the game is “no longer a dream”. Suc
 h big lofty words.\n\nPerhaps the biggest difference is that there are no 
 longer the 2 opposing factions\, Elyos and Asmodians (due to the timeline)
 . Players are free to choose to invade others of defend. Another eye-opene
 r is the claim of not having “class segmentation” in Aion 2\, with players
  able to wield different weapons without restrictions and choose their pla
 ystyle. NCsoft claims that Aion 2 will “showcase a new battle system that 
 did not exist in the old Aion”.\n\nFinally\, another huge change is the re
 moval of gliding constraints found in Aion. While this was not explained i
 n detail\, NCsoft is aiming to make gliding part of the combat loop to cre
 ate a “three dimensional battle system”. NCsoft did not mention what engin
 e Aion 2 is developed on\, but my guess is Unreal Engine 5. Stay tuned for
  more updates on the game!\n\nhttps://www.igdb.com/games/aion-2
END:VEVENT
