BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:8a55255f74b405b87cca605a32d0b0543fe96b61@overworld-igdb-sync
DTSTAMP:20260706T210613Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261231
SUMMARY:Skyblivion (PC (Microsoft Windows))
DESCRIPTION:Skyblivion is the ultimate fan-made experience for the Elder Sc
 rolls IV: Oblivion\, bringing the game into the newer engine of the Elder 
 Scrolls V: Skyrim. This process combines Oblivion’s impressive award-winni
 ng open-world that is renowned for its incredible gameplay\, memorable que
 sts\, and expansive world space with the advancements in gaming that have 
 been made in the last two decades. Set in the Elder Scroll’s Third Era\, d
 uring the cataclysmic Oblivion Crisis\, you must help to restore the Imper
 ial throne and repel the demonic Daedric invasion.\n\nSkyblivion will feat
 ure the remastered entirety of Oblivion’s mainland\, Cyrodiil\, from the w
 intery slopes of the Valus and Jerall Mountains to the swamps of Blackwood
  and warm-beachy shores of the Gold Coast. Skyblivion will bring the retur
 n of many classic Oblivion mechanics like spell crafting\, a complete clas
 s and attributes system\, underwater combat\, and NPC disposition.\n\nIn a
 ddition to recreating Oblivion’s systems and porting them into the Elder S
 crolls V: Skyrim’s engine the project has taken great care in providing ne
 w improvements and additions. Skyblivion offers fans remastered graphics\,
  weather\, and lighting\, an expanded soundtrack\, new gameplay mechanics\
 , and even a limited selection of bespoke minor quests with original voice
  acting to further flesh out barren areas of Oblivion—all for free!\n\nOnc
 e Skyblivion is released in 2025\, fans will have access to the entirety o
 f Oblivion’s pre-DLC world space\, systems\, and quests available for play
 . But that’s not the end of the project! Following a period of bug-fixing 
 and community-supported updates the project development team will move on 
 to working on Oblivion’s nine additional content releases plus the Shiveri
 ng Isles expansion.\n\nWith Skyblivion you experience the best of both wor
 lds: The complex and detailed RPG experience of Oblivion paired with Skyri
 m’s newer systems\, graphics\, and quality of life improvements. Will you 
 close shut the jaws of Oblivion once more in 2025?\n\nhttps://www.igdb.com
 /games/skyblivion
END:VEVENT
