SUMMARY:Nightborn (PC (Microsoft Windows))
DESCRIPTION:Nightborn is an Action RPG with narrative-focused gameplay set 
 in a dark gothic version of our own world.\nPlayers assume the role of the
  Bloodhound\, a Vampire detective trained in tracking supernatural threats
  to the Nightborn\, using arcane rituals forbidden to others of your kind.
 \nInvestigate a series of disappearances of your fellow Vampires\, includi
 ng your Maker\, a politically influential member of the Nightborn\, the Va
 mpire elite of New Orleans.\n\nCreate your own Bloodhound character\, choo
 sing from 10 iconic Vampire lineages with a set of signature lineage power
  skill trees.\n\nLineage powers include physical prowess enhancements\, sh
 apeshifting\, controlling the minds of mortals\, and acts of eldritch sorc
 ery.\n\nFuel Vampire powers by preying upon mortals via stealth\, seductio
 n\, or brute force.\n\nElude Mortal Law Enforcement and Monster Hunters\, 
 masking your dark nature.\n\nSolve the mysteries of gothic New Orleans by 
 taking quests\, discovering clues\, and exploring the supernatural underwo
 rld.\n\nBattle\, evade\, or outwit\, natural and supernatural foes\, using
  your powers\, weapons\, and tactics.\n\nSide with a Nightborn faction\, t
 he ruling Establishment\, the reckless Libertines\, or the fanatical Ortho
 doxy\; or eschew them all to forge your own path.\n\nhttps://www.igdb.com/
 games/nightborn
END:VEVENT
