SUMMARY:RockBeasts (Nintendo Switch\, PlayStation 5\, Xbox Series X|S)
DESCRIPTION:Lead a band of misfits on a roller-coaster ride to stardom in t
 he age of MTV\, rock anthems\, and bad haircuts. ROCKBEASTS is a story-dri
 ven\, role-playing management game that puts you in the shoes of a manager
  of an up-and-coming rock band.\n\nRock ‘n’ Roll Band Manager: This band h
 as real potential\, but they need your help to live up to it. Their tunes 
 can revolutionize the music industry and redefine genres - but what good i
 s a great song if no one hears it? It’s your job to land your clients a re
 cord deal and negotiate the terms on their behalf. Will you help them figh
 t for their creative freedom\, or sell them out to the industry bigwigs?\n
 \nCoffee and Cigarettes for Breakfast: Sex\, drugs\, and rock ’n’ roll can
  only get you so far. Somebody has to make sure the band is in shape to pl
 ay the next gig. This is where you come in. Make sure they eat a half-dece
 nt meal every now and again\, fix their gear\, get them to rehearse… Hope 
 you like herding cats!\n\nDon’t Stop Me Now: It’s your job to book the ven
 ue\, finalize the setlist and ensure the gig goes according to the plan. E
 ach successful performance is a step toward fame and glory. Sure\, that “c
 lub” was just a grimy basement\, and the audience barely outnumbered the b
 and - but even rock legends have to start somewhere\, right?\n\nhttps://ww
 w.igdb.com/games/rockbeasts
