SUMMARY:Red Rust Pioneers (PC (Microsoft Windows))
DESCRIPTION:Your story begins stranded in the unforgiving wilderness of the
  Wild West.\n\nYour one goal: to survive.\n\nEndure scorching days and fre
 ezing nights as you battle hunger\, thirst\, and the elements. Forage for 
 food\, hunt wildlife\, and fish to stay alive. Scavenge the land to gather
  vital resources and craft the tools and weapons you’ll need to stand a ch
 ance in this brutal but breathtaking frontier.\n\nCan you master the eleme
 nts and withstand blistering heat\, violent rainstorms and freezing cold w
 inters?\n\nShould you beat the odds and live\, alone or with up to three f
 riends\, you’ll find yourself in a gorgeous\, rugged\, vibrant land. Will 
 you be able to not only survive\, but thrive?\n\nBuild and grow your camp 
 your way with easy to use base building mechanics. Fish in the lakes and r
 ivers\, or hunt in the atmospheric woodlands and open prairies. Farm and h
 arvest a variety of crops to establish a self-sufficient camp. Adventure h
 igh into the mountains to mine resources\, and craft better weapons and to
 ols.\n\nExplore a beautifully realized\, open world\, fictionalized Wild W
 est frontier and become the first to discover the untamed wilderness of Re
 d Rust Valley.\n\nIf you can overcome the threat of extreme hunger\, bruta
 l weather conditions and lethal wildlife you may just live to appreciate i
 t.\n\nhttps://www.igdb.com/games/red-rust-pioneers
END:VEVENT
