SUMMARY:Sniper Dan (PC (Microsoft Windows))
DESCRIPTION:Meet Dan. Dan has a sniper rifle. Don’t panic\, he’s not here t
 o harm anyone. Dan’s a professional and his job is fixing things. From a d
 istance. With pinpoint accuracy and good intentions.\n\nSniper Dan is a hi
 dden object game unlike any other. Objects aren’t always well hidden and t
 he solution involves shooting them. Each job follows a simple and highly r
 espected method.\n\n1. Figure out the problem. Use the clues. HMM…\n2. Fin
 d the problem. Scope the area. AHA!\n3. Fix the problem. Shoot. WHEE!\n\nY
 ou’re not hunting enemies. You’re hunting problems. Fixing rusty taps\, ma
 chines behaving badly\, and even stop a thieving Pelican. Travel far and w
 ide across lively 3D locations packed with visual jokes and silly situatio
 ns as you help those in need. Can Dan and his trusty tool get the job done
 ?\n\nDan’s business takes him to villages\, parks\, farms\, airports\, cit
 ies\, and beyond. Special challenges keep every day fresh. Take on optiona
 l work for extra cash\, tackle bigger jobs for even bigger rewards\, and u
 ncover secrets that leave citizens quietly convinced something magical jus
 t happened.\n\nIt did. It was Dan!\n\nBetween contracts\, upgrade your rif
 le\, decorate your office hub\, and grow your entirely legitimate troubles
 hooting business. Unlock bonus games and extra modes like Time Attack\, Am
 mo Hunt\, and Photo Mode\, all under the judgmental eye of Rank Chook.\n\n
 Funny\, colorful\, and sure to leave you wanting more\, Sniper Dan is abou
 t finding what’s wrong\, fixing it fast\, and moving on to the next job.\n
 \nScope the problem. Take the shot. Make everyone happy.\n\nhttps://www.ig
 db.com/games/sniper-dan
END:VEVENT
