SUMMARY:Szkeletal (PC (Microsoft Windows))
DESCRIPTION:Szkeletal: Estrogen Dracul's Potato Hunger (also known by its o
 riginal Polish title: SZKELETAL: Ziemniaczkowy Głód Estrogenowego Drakula)
  is a 2D top-down action roguelite and bullet heaven game heavily inspired
  by the gameplay loop of titles like Vampire Survivors. It serves as a sat
 irical parody of the Polish internet\, specifically targeting the gaming c
 ommunity\, local content creators\, and self-proclaimed "ludologists".\n\n
 Set in a vaguely defined\, fictionalized location\, loosely inspired by th
 e internet lore of personalities fleeing to Romania. Players take control 
 of the titular "Estrogen Dracul". The core gameplay involves collecting po
 tatoes and automatically attacking hordes of meme-based enemies. Key featu
 res include the "Destiny Cards" system\, which allows players to manually 
 pick up and throw cards to trigger specific tactical effects\, as well as 
 a dynamic weather and day/night cycle that actively modifies visibility du
 ring runs.\n\nhttps://www.igdb.com/games/szkeletal
END:VEVENT
