SUMMARY:Shatterswarm (PC (Microsoft Windows))
DESCRIPTION:Shatterswarm is a narrative-driven 2D space shooter that combin
 es direct ship combat\, fleet command\, tower defense\, and base building 
 into a strategic colony survival experience. Command Captain Hope's hero s
 hip as you defend Earth's last bastion\, The Citadel\, against the relentl
 ess Voxan Empire.\n\nTake control of your hero ship in intense 2D space co
 mbat while simultaneously building and managing a fleet of ships\, constru
 cting defensive networks around your citadel\, and managing resources to s
 urvive wave after wave of alien invaders. Every decision matters as you ba
 lance offensive capabilities with defensive structures\, all while facing 
 unique enemy types that require different strategies to defeat.\n\nThe gam
 e features a diverse roster of challenging enemies\, each with distinct me
 chanics: parasites that hack into and take control of your own ships\, mot
 herships that spawn smaller vessels\, deflectors that fire your projectile
 s back at you\, and robotic enemies that latch onto your ships and tear th
 em apart. Face off against epic multi-phase boss battles against Voxan com
 manders Gordox\, Gudrak\, and the dreaded General Mortex.\n\nWith its perf
 ect blend of action\, strategy\, and base building\, Shatterswarm offers a
  unique short game experience where tactical thinking and quick reflexes a
 re both essential for survival. The Citadel's survival depends on your str
 ategy—will you focus on overwhelming firepower\, impenetrable defenses\, o
 r a balanced approach?\n\nhttps://www.igdb.com/games/shatterswarm
END:VEVENT
