 orgiving. Weapons are primitive. Injuries matter. There are no easy victor
 ies.\n\nAlong the way\, Kiipluu is haunted by dreamlike spirit journeys an
 d visions of his father\, a legendary hunter whose shadow looms over every
  choice. Your decisions shape who survives\, who is lost\, and what kind o
